tip.text: The atmosphere, service and food were all divine. Cosy and quick and each plate served with a description and full of flavour. The pumpkin ravioli with chestnuts was delicious, the cauliflower - Yum!
The spa and the bathrobes are great! Hot tub after ski is perfect and the service in the restaurants has been amazing. The mountains are amazing and there is plenty to do for large groups.
